# Course 2 station env. Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and edit.

# Live inference server (server/ — see server/README.md). OPT-IN: when unset,
# every station uses precomputed JSON exactly as before. When set, the
# embedding / next-token / rnn-viz / transformer / order-shuffle stations send
# CUSTOM student input to the server (the same real models that recorded the
# preset artifacts) and fall back to precomputed data whenever the server is
# unreachable.
#
# There is NO client token: access is gated by a shared password students type
# into the login popup, which the server exchanges for an HttpOnly session
# cookie (see server/app/auth.py). Nothing secret ships in the bundle.
#VITE_LIVE_INFERENCE_URL=http://localhost:8300
